			<deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">The inventory data, including the material consumption andenvironmental emissions involved in the production of solar-gradesilicon, wafers, ingots, cells, and modules, were mainly collectedfrom companies that represent the current domain multi-Si PVtechnologies in China. The energy consumption data referred to thereport “Clean Production ofSolar PV in China” (Li and Chang, 2012).The data of MG-Si production was from literature about MG-Siproduced in China</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">库存数据，包括太阳能级产品生产过程中的材料消耗和 太阳能级硅、硅片、硅锭、电池和组件生产过程中的材料消耗和环境排放 硅、硅片、硅锭、电池和组件生产过程中涉及的材料消耗和环境排放。主要从代表中国目前多晶硅光伏技术领域的企业收集。技术的企业。能耗数据参考了 能耗数据参考了《中国太阳能光伏清洁生产报告》（Li 和 Chang，2012 年）。多晶硅生产数据来自有关中国多晶硅生产的文献。的文献资料。</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<referenceToDataSource type="source data set" refObjectId="e5f8a793-a35e-41c2-aad3-12c44660d71b" uri="../sources/e5f8a793-a35e-41c2-aad3-12c44660d71b.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en"> Fu, Y., Liu, X. &amp; Yuan, Z. Life-cycle assessment of multi-crystalline photovoltaic (PV) systems in China. Journal of Cleaner Production 86, 180–190 (2015).</common:shortDescription>
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh"> Fu, Y., Liu, X. &amp; Yuan, Z. Life-cycle assessment of multi-crystalline photovoltaic (PV) systems in China. Journal of Cleaner Production 86, 180–190 (2015).</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing the life-cycle assessment data for multi-Si PV modules in China, it is essential to integrate the material consumption and environmental emissions as outlined in this inventory data for the complete production process, from silicon to the final module assembly. Additionally, users should consider the energy consumption benchmarks from the 'Clean Production of Solar PV in China' report. The data set is optimized for assessing the environmental impacts in the Chinese context and should be used accordingly. It is paramount to use the functional unit of 1 kWh of multi-Si PV module output when evaluating lifecycle impacts to ensure comparability.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用中国多晶硅光伏模块的生命周期评估数据时，必须整合此库存数据中列出的从硅料到最终模块组装的完整生产过程中的材料消耗和环境排放。此外，用户应该考虑《中国太阳能光伏清洁生产报告》中的能耗基准。此数据集针对评估中国环境影响进行了优化，并应相应使用。在评估生命周期影响时，使用1 kWh多晶硅光伏模块输出的功能单位至关重要，以确保可比性。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
